  "texts": [
    "The mean squared error (MSE) loss was used for model training.",
    "For the molecular dynamic dataset including MD17, rMD17, MD22, and Chignolin, we leveraged a combined MSE loss for energy and force prediction.",
    "The weight of energy loss was set to 0.05.",
    "The weight of force loss was set to 0.95.",
    "The batch size was chosen from 2, 4, 8 due to the GPU memory and the learning rate was chosen from 1e-4 to 4e-4 for different molecules."
  ],
